author: ETA PRIME
description:
The ROG Ally and Ally X just got TWO major performance updates — one from ASUS and one straight from Xbox — and these changes make a huge difference for real-world gameplay. Armoury Crate SE 1.15 adds core-control tuning, better FPS limiter behavior, fullscreen keybinds, and more. But the biggest news is the new Xbox Default Game Profiles, which intelligently adjust TDP per game to boost FPS or save battery automatically.
